sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as Orion UI
    participant Wizard as BYO Wizard
    participant Backend as Orion Backend
    participant KC as Keycloak
    participant RHAO as Red Hat Agent Operator
    participant K8s as Kubernetes
    participant Pod as Agent Pod

    User->>UI: Click "+ New Agent"
    UI->>UI: Open Intent Dialog
    User->>UI: Select "BYO Agent"
    UI->>Wizard: Open CreateAgentWizard

    Note over Wizard: Step 1 - Basics
    Wizard->>Backend: GET /kagenti/namespaces
    Backend->>RHAO: GET /api/v1/namespaces
    RHAO-->>Backend: [namespaces]
    Backend-->>Wizard: Namespace dropdown populated
    User->>Wizard: Enter name, namespace, framework

    Note over Wizard: Step 2 - Deployment
    User->>Wizard: Select "Container Image"
    User->>Wizard: Enter image URL + pull secret

    Note over Wizard: Step 3 - Runtime
    User->>Wizard: Add env vars, ports, toggles
    User->>Wizard: Click "Create"

    Note over Wizard,Pod: Agent Creation
    Wizard->>Backend: POST /kagenti/agents
    Backend->>Backend: Validate namespace
    Backend->>KC: client_credentials grant
    KC-->>Backend: Access token (with audience scopes)
    Backend->>RHAO: POST /api/v1/agents (Bearer token)
    RHAO->>K8s: Create Deployment
    RHAO->>K8s: Create Service
    RHAO->>K8s: Create Route
    RHAO-->>Backend: {success: true}
    Backend->>Backend: Auto-register in chatAgents (draft)
    Backend-->>Wizard: Agent created

    Wizard->>UI: Close wizard, refresh My Agents
    K8s->>Pod: Schedule + pull image
    Pod->>Pod: Start agent server (port 8000)

    Note over UI,Pod: Agent Ready
    UI->>UI: Agent appears in My Agents (Draft)
    User->>UI: Click agent > Test tab
    UI->>Backend: POST /chat/stream (model=ns/name)
    Backend->>KC: Get/refresh token
    Backend->>RHAO: POST /api/v1/chat/ns/name/stream
    RHAO->>Pod: Forward request (A2A protocol)
    Pod-->>RHAO: SSE response
    RHAO-->>Backend: Stream events
    Backend-->>UI: stream.text.delta events
    UI->>UI: Display agent response
